📍 @7Pinesibiza @Hyatt @Destinationhotels

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure!

node.text:
Gorgeous resort views by @caracarl at the Laucala Island Resort. 🏝 This private tropical paradise nestled among coconut plantations is your ultimate social distancing destination in the South Pacific! 🇫🇯

Thinking of exploring this island resort? Laucala's activities range from relaxing to adventurous. Tee off at their golf course which was thoughtfully designed to be integrated with the land's natural curves. Head to the Dive Centre and begin your journey to meet angelfish and hawksbill turtles while snorkeling, and end your day at the Spa Garden for some holistic therapy! 💆‍♀️

Have you been to Laucala? Is Fiji on your bucket list? ✈

📸 @caracarl
📍@laucalaisland, Fiji

node.text:
Be mesmerized by centuries-old views like @michaeltheexplorer at the Marvel Stone Hotel. 🇪🇬 Located across the street from the Entrance of Giza, the hotel offers spectacular views of the Three Great Pyramids & the Sphinx from its rooftop. How's this for a morning view? ❤️

Curious about pyramids? Here are some awesome facts about them!
1. The pyramids were once the tallest human-built structures.
2. There are actually more than a hundred pyramids in Egypt!
3. The Great Pyramid of Giza weighs an estimated 5,750,000 tons. 
4. Not all pyramids are pointed! 
5. We still don't know why they were built, but there are so many theories!

Have you visited the Great Pyramids? Is Egypt on your bucket list? 

📸 @michaeltheexplorer
📍 @marvelstonehotel, Cairo, Egypt

node.text:
Let @oddproduzioni give you eco-glamping vibes at Iuta Glamping and Farm! 🍃 A glamour camping stay with luxury lodges, it's a serene retreat where you're fully surrounded by the natural beauty of century-old olive trees and a lemon plantation. 😍 

Being here will give you the feeling of living in full contact with the nature that surrounds you without having to give up on any comfort. The camp also adopts an eco-sustainable lifestyle and doesn’t use chemicals products. If you're aiming for an environment-friendly vacation, Iuta should definitely be at the top of your list! 🌱

Are eco-stays something you'd want to experience? Would you stay here? 

📸 @oddproduzioni
📍 @iutafarm, Syracuse, Italy

Indulge in elevated resort-living at the @longbaybvi. 🏝 Located in the heart of the British Virgin Islands, the resort brings a hip and fresh take on the island lifestyle that highlights its stunning natural surroundings and ocean views. 🐚

Long Bay Beach Resort is located on a mile of white sand and Caribbean waters—your perfect aquatic playground for surfing, kayaking, and snorkeling! 🤿 Ready to explore coral reefs and nearby islands with the resort's own speedboat?

Once you've worked up an appetite, satisfy your cravings with exquisite food sourced from their own organic garden and enjoy a mojito at their cocktail bar. 🍹

With their top-tier and bespoke customer service, your stay at Long Bay Beach Resort will truly be special. Who are you bringing with you to experience this laidback tropical luxury? 🌊

node.text:
Fall in love with this perfect getaway with @moroccanmusthaves! 😍 Located in Essaouira, Villa Anouk is built in the ancient Moroccan Beldi tradition, made entirely of stone and wood with thatched ceilings by local artisans and master craftsmen. The result is a stunning retreat that serves as a perfect base to explore the town, but also to relax and bliss out in the beautiful setting. 🇲🇦

💡 BH Tip: Villa Anouk is a prime spot for authentic Berber cooking and shouldn't be missed! If ever you're going out to explore the town and find yourself in Moulay Bouzerktoun, Villa Anouk recommends Lamawa Restaurant!

When was the last time you visited Morocco? What was your best experience here? 

📸 @moroccanmusthaves
📍 @villaanouk, Essaouira, Morocco

Be among the first to experience timeless glamour and modern sophistication as The Langham Jakarta finally opens its doors to welcome you with its legendary Langham service and hospitality that has won loyal patrons worldwide for 150 years. ✨

2. Indulge in culinary masterpieces at their Michelin Starred restaurants: Tom’s by Tom Aikens and T’ang Court. 😋 
3. Work remotely at The Langham Club Lounge and fuel your productivity with its amenities.
4. Have afternoon tea at Alice. 🍵 
5. Drink cocktails at Artisan, located on their rooftop, where the best views of the city and sunsets can be enjoyed.
6. End your day with a rubdown at Chuan Spa. 💆🏼‍♀️ 
7. Retire for the night in one of the 223 guest rooms all lavishly furnished and spacious to suit your taste.

Celebrate The Everday at The Langham, Jakarta. ❤️

📍 @delimakmur @langham_jakarta and @langhamhotels
